  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Keep 1000 Ugandan Girls in School</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Only through educational and vocational training can girls in developing countries change their future.  The #1 reasons girls in Uganda drop out of school is their monthly cycle.  This project provides a sustainable and eco-friendly solution: reusable sanitary pads. In addition, girls will receive vocational training and learn how to make the pads themselves, which they will share with other girls in a pay-it-forward community outreach.</narrative>
  </description>
